<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[118, 117, 473, 136]]<|/det|>
Give the answer correct to 3 decimal places.

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[890, 117, 920, 136]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[156, 73, 777, 92]]<|/det|>
Show that the equation \(\sin 2\theta + \cos 2\theta = 2\sin^2\theta\) can be expressed in the form

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[358, 100, 636, 120]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[890, 101, 920, 120]]<|/det|>
<mark>[2]

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[109, 390, 143, 408]]<|/det|>
<label>(b)</label>

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[154, 390, 710, 408]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[890, 390, 920, 408]]<|/det|>
<mark>[4]
